            "text": "<p>The work on the blue velvet suit is truly beautiful. The intricate work stands out, and the fabric feels fine and of good quality. Overall, it’s an elegant and well-made piece, perfect for special occasions</p><p><strong>~ Mudita</strong><br/></p>",
