    "custom_liquid_NfHqM8": {
      "type": "custom-liquid",
      "custom_css": [
        "{width: 85%; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;}"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "<p><strong>Stylish Kurta Sets and Ethnic Wear for Women</strong><br><br>Kurta sets are a staple in Indian women&apos;s wardrobes, often becoming the go-to choice for traditional events like weddings, festivals, casual parties, formal gatherings, and get-togethers. With a wide selection of patterns, designs, and colors, our brand offers high-quality kurta sets at affordable prices. Explore a diverse range of printed kurta sets and two-piece ensembles from Sitarah, available in sizes from XS to 3XL, including customize-size options. Our latest collection features kurta sets with a variety of bottoms, such as palazzo dupatta suit sets, pants, trousers, and leggings, all highly sought after. Kurta sets for weddings and festivals are a perfect addition to your wardrobe during this festive season.<br><br><strong>Shop Sitarah&apos;s Most-Loved 3-Piece Sets</strong><br><br>Discover stunning kurta sets from Sitarah, featuring unique designs paired with stylish bottoms and dupattas in vibrant patterns and colors that will make you stand out on any occasion. Browse through www.sitarah.in to find your perfect set, whether it&rsquo;s printed kurta sets, Anarkali suit sets, party wear, or cotton kurtas. Choose from a beautiful color palette ranging from black, green, sage, mint green, aqua, red, yellow, and more. Whether you prefer pastels or bright tones, add exquisitely crafted pieces to your wardrobe with Sitarah.<br><br><strong>Comfortable Palazzo Kurta Sets for Everyday and Special Occasions</strong><br><br>Sitarah&apos;s kurta sets feature delicate details and intricate craftsmanship, offering a perfect blend of style and comfort from morning to evening. Explore our collection of daily wear kurta sets, as well as elegant evening and occasion wear in rich chanderi and embellished fabrics. For special occasions like festivals, family gatherings, or weddings, our luxe collection includes chanderi suit sets, silk blends, mull, chiffon, and more. Complete your look by pairing your ethnic kurta set with matching accessories, jewelry in antique or gold finishes, colorful accents, and complementing footwear. Don&rsquo;t forget to add the perfect handbag to elevate your style.<br><br>Explore the latest kurta sets, designer collections, sharara sets, and more on the Sitarah website. With a perfect blend of comfort and timeless ethnic styles, Sitarah is your one-stop destination for all your wardrobe needs.</p>",
        "color_scheme": "",
        "padding_top": 20,
        "padding_bottom": 20
      }
    }
  },
